  "records": {
    "description": "Simple SS3 filtered compactor with optional Loader version if needed.",
    "features": [
      "No prefill required",
      "Box Loader Version available"
    ],
    "considerations": [
      "no SSI possible",
      "3 dusts (but lag is mitigated by green SS2 Line)",
      "No crafter recovery (needs to be cleaned out manually if crafter overflows)"
    ],
    "notes": "We still suggest you build https://discord.com/channels/856232076252282890/1304491479691034715 if you need more than 3x of speed. also having a loader at each compactor is mostly unnecessary since the hopper speed gets reduced by 9 allowing a 162/h item stream satisfy a single 2x loader"
